title: Growth Principles Of The Devil

status: Mó jiào jiàozhǔ de chéng cháng fǎzé ; Mo Jiao Jiao Zhu De Cheng Chang Fa Ze ; 魔教教主的成长法则

description:
Description :
        Su Qingyu is a hobbyist gamer and a guild leader in an MMO game. However, after a successful boss raid, Qingyu is transported into the MMO game itself. There is only one way to return to the real world – becoming a “Devilish Cult Leader”. How will things play out?
